## Cloudflare Web Analytics Privacy Features

✅ **No cookies** - No client-side state stored
✅ **No fingerprinting** - No individual user tracking
✅ **No cross-site tracking** - Data doesn't follow users
✅ **IP addresses anonymized** - By Cloudflare automatically
✅ **GDPR/CCPA compliant** - Designed for privacy regulations
✅ **Aggregate data only** - Page views, referrers, device types (not personal)

